                            start=configs['data']['task1_train_start'],
                            cols=configs['data']['columns'],
                            time_flag=configs['data']['time_flag']['task1_train'],
                            scaler=scaler)
In [6]:
# get the features and labels

                                device=device,
                                mode_flag=configs['data']['mode']['train'])
In [7]:
# we use quantile loss as our criterion
loss_func = QuantileLoss(configs['model']['quantiles'])
In [8]:
# define the learning rate and alpha
learning_rate = [1, 3, 5, 9]
a = 0.99
In [9]:
# SGD online model
for lr in learning_rate:
    seed_torch()
    model_SGD = LSTM(configs=configs,
                     device=device,
                     loss_function=loss_func,
                     scaler=scaler).to(device)
    optimizer_SGD = SGD(model_SGD.parameters(), lr=lr)
    SGD_losses, SGD_times = model_SGD.train_online(x, y, optimizer_SGD)

    np.savetxt('SGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '.txt', SGD_losses)
    np.savetxt('SGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_times.txt', SGD_times)

# SGD offline model
for lr in learning_rate:
    seed_torch()
    model_SGD = LSTM(configs=configs,
                     device=device,
                     loss_function=loss_func,
                     scaler=scaler).to(device)
    optimizer_SGD = SGD(model_SGD.parameters(), lr=lr)
    # SGD_losses, SGD_times = model_SGD.train_online_benchmark(x, y, validation_x, validation_y, optimizer_SGD)
    SGD_losses, SGD_times = model_SGD.train_offline(x, y, optimizer_SGD)

    np.savetxt('SGD_offline_lr=' + str(lr) + '.txt', SGD_losses)
    np.savetxt('SGD_offline_lr=' + str(lr) + '_times.txt', SGD_times)

learning_rate = [1, 3, 5, 7, 9]

In [12]:
# PTS-SGD online model
for lr in learning_rate:
    for w in window_size:
        seed_torch()
        model_online = LSTM(configs=configs,
                            device=device,
                            loss_function=loss_func,
                            scaler=scaler).to(device)
        optimizer_PTSSGD = PTSSGD(model_online.parameters(), lr=lr, window_size=w, a=a)
        PTSSGD_losses, PTSSGD_times = model_online.train_online(x, y, optimizer_PTSSGD)

        np.savetxt('PTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.txt', PTSSGD_losses)
        np.savetxt('PTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '_times.txt', PTSSGD_times)
In [13]:
# HTS-SGD model
for lr in learning_rate:
    for w in window_size:
        seed_torch()
        model_HTSSGD = LSTM(configs=configs,
                          device=device,
                          loss_function=loss_func,
                          scaler=scaler).to(device)
        optimizer_HTSSGD = HTSSGD(model_HTSSGD.parameters(), lr=lr)
        HTSSGD_losses, HTSSGD_times = model_HTSSGD.train_online_hsgd(x, y, w, optimizer_HTSSGD)

        np.savetxt('HTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.txt', HTSSGD_losses)
        np.savetxt('HTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '_times.txt', HTSSGD_times)

In [15]:
#  plot HTS-SGD results
for w in window_size:
    HSGD_online_losses_1 = np.loadtxt('HTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(1) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.txt')
    HSGD_online_losses_3 = np.loadtxt('HTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(3) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.txt')
    HSGD_online_losses_5 = np.loadtxt('HTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(5) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.txt')
    HSGD_online_losses_7 = np.loadtxt('HTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(7) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.txt')
    HSGD_online_losses_9 = np.loadtxt('HTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(9) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.txt')

    plt.figure()
    plt.plot(HSGD_online_losses_1, 'r-', label=r'$\eta$ = 1', lw=1.5)
    plt.plot(HSGD_online_losses_3, 'b-', label=r'$\eta$ = 3', lw=1.5)
    plt.plot(HSGD_online_losses_5, 'y-', label=r'$\eta$ = 5', lw=1.5)
    plt.plot(HSGD_online_losses_7, 'g-', label=r'$\eta$ = 7', lw=1.5)
    plt.plot(HSGD_online_losses_9, 'm-', label=r'$\eta$ = 9', lw=1.5)
    plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(MaxNLocator(integer=True))
    plt.xlabel('New observed datasets', fontsize=25)
    plt.ylabel(r'$QL_{grand}$', fontsize=25)
    plt.legend(loc='upper right', fontsize=16)
    plt.yscale('log')
    plt.grid(True, which='both')
    plt.tick_params(labelsize=17)
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.ylim(ymin, ymax)
    plt_save = 'HTSSGD_online_with_different_lr_and_w_=_' + str(w) + '.png'

    plt.savefig(plt_save)
    plt.show()

# comparison the outputs of 4 models with different learning rates when window size is 200
for lr in learning_rate:
    for w in window_size:
        SGD_online_losses = np.loadtxt('SGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '.txt')
        SGD_online_benchmark_losses = np.loadtxt('SGD_offline_lr=' + str(lr) + '.txt')
        TSSGD_online_losses = np.loadtxt('PTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.txt')
        HSGD_online_losses = np.loadtxt('HTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.txt')

        plt.figure()
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(MaxNLocator(integer=True))
        plt.plot(SGD_online_losses, 'k-', label='SGD online', lw=3)
        plt.plot(SGD_online_benchmark_losses, 'g-', label='SGD offline', lw=3)
        plt.plot(TSSGD_online_losses, 'r-', label='PTS-SGD online', lw=3)
        plt.plot(HSGD_online_losses, 'y-', label='HTS-SGD online', lw=3)
        plt.xlabel('New observed datasets', fontsize=25)
        plt.ylabel(r'$QL_{grand}$', fontsize=25)
        plt.legend(loc='upper right', fontsize=16)
        plt.yscale('log')
        plt.grid(True, which='both')
        plt.tick_params(labelsize=17)
        plt.tight_layout()
        plt.ylim(ymin, ymax)
        plt.savefig('Comparison_QL_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.png')
        plt.show()

In [20]:
# comparison the time spent of 4 models with different window size when learning rate is 9
for lr in learning_rate:
    for w in window_size:
        SGD_online_times = []
        SGD_online_benchmark_times = []
        TSSGD_online_times = []
        HSGD_online_times = []

        SGD_online_time = np.loadtxt('SGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_times.txt')
        SGD_offline_time = np.loadtxt('SGD_offline_lr=' + str(lr) + '_times.txt')
        PTSSGD_online_time = np.loadtxt('PTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '_times.txt')
        HTSSGD_online_time = np.loadtxt('HTSSGD_online_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '_times.txt')

        for i in range(len(SGD_online_time)):
            SGD_online_times.append(sum(SGD_online_time[:i + 1]))
            SGD_online_benchmark_times.append(sum(SGD_offline_time[:i + 1]))
            TSSGD_online_times.append(sum(PTSSGD_online_time[:i + 1]))
            HSGD_online_times.append(sum(HTSSGD_online_time[:i + 1]))

        plt.figure()
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(MaxNLocator(integer=True))
        plt.plot(SGD_online_times, 'k-', label='SGD online', lw=3)
        plt.plot(SGD_online_benchmark_times, 'g-', label='SGD offline', lw=3)
        plt.plot(TSSGD_online_times, 'r-', label='PTS-SGD online', lw=3)
        plt.plot(HSGD_online_times, 'y-', label='HTS-SGD online', lw=3)
        plt.xlabel('New observed datasets', fontsize=25)
        plt.ylabel('GPU seconds', fontsize=25)
        plt.legend(loc='best', fontsize=16)
        plt.grid(True, which='both')
        plt.tick_params(labelsize=17)
        plt.tight_layout()
        plt.ylim(0, 80)
        plt.savefig('Comparison_time_lr=' + str(lr) + '_w=' + str(w) + '.png')
        plt.show()
